#: index.docbook:8
msgid "Useful tips"
msgstr "Iincam eziluncedo"

#: index.docbook:13
msgid "Reading man pages in &kde;"
msgstr "Ifunda amaphepha omntu kwi &kde;"

#: index.docbook:16
msgid ""
"Pop up the minicli window (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> by default) and type "
"<command>man:<replaceable>command</replaceable></command>. It even unpacks "
"on the fly if the man pages are gzipped."
msgstr ""
"Jonga iminicli window (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> ngokungagqibekanga) no "
"didi <command>umntuy:<replaceable>umyalelo</replaceable></command>. "
"Ayipakishi kubhabho ukuba amaphepha omntu a gzipped."

#: index.docbook:21
msgid ""
"Or you can use the <application>&kde; Help Center</application> if you are "
"using &kde; 2. Simply start the <application>&kde; Help Center</application>"
" by clicking on the icon (the blue book with the yellow key) on the toolbar. "
"Once the <application>&kde; Help Center</application>"
" has loaded, the window on the left will contain an entry called "
"<guilabel>Unix manual pages</guilabel>. Click once on this entry, and you "
"can browse through all the installed manual pages on your system."
msgstr ""
"Okanye ungasebenzisa i <application>&kde; Umbindi Woncedo</application> "
"ukuba usebenzisa i &kde; 2. Qala ngokucacileyo i <application>&kde; Umbindi "
"Woncedo</application> ngokunqakraza kwi icon (incwadi eluhlaza enesitshixo "
"esimthubi) kwibar yesixhobo. Xa i <application>&kde; Umbindi "
"Wolawulo</application> ulayishe, iwindow ekhohlo izakuqulatha ungeno "
"olubizwa nge <guilabel>Unix amaphepha encwadi</guilabel>. Nqakraza kanye "
"kolu ngeno, kwaye ungakhangela ngapha kwawo wonke amaphepha afakiweyo "
"encwadi kwindlela yakho."

#: index.docbook:33
msgid "Move or resize windows quickly"
msgstr "Shukuma okanye linganisela kwakhona iiwindow ngokukhawuleza"

#: index.docbook:36
msgid ""
"To move a window, use <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<mousebutton>left</mousebutton></keycombo> mouse "
"button. <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<mousebutton>right</mousebutton></keycombo> mouse "
"button will resize the window. Last but not least, <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<mousebutton>middle</mousebutton></keycombo> mouse "
"button raises/lowers the window. The <application>&kde; Control "
"Center</application> allows you to change these mouse bindings."
msgstr ""
"Ukushukumisa iwindow , sebenzisa i <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<mousebutton>ekhohlo</mousebutton></keycombo> iqhosha "
"le mouse. <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<mousebutton>ekunene</mousebutton></keycombo> iqhosha "
"le mouse lizakulinganisela iwidow kwakhona. Okokugqibela kodwa "
"okungakuncinananga, <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<mousebutton>phakathi</mousebutton></keycombo>"
" iqhosha le mouse linyusa/lihlisa iwindow. I <application>&kde; Umbindi "
"Wolawulo</application> ukuvumela utshintshe ezi zibophelelo ze mouse."

#: index.docbook:49
msgid "Killing windows in &kde;"
msgstr "Ibulala iiwindow kwi &kde;"

#: index.docbook:52
msgid ""
"There is a standard keybinding (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Esc;</keycombo>) that gives you a "
"skull/crossbones cursor. Click that cursor on a window to kill it. The "
"keybindings are viewable/changeable from the <application>&kde; Control "
"Center</application>."
msgstr ""
"Kukho isibophelelo esingundoqo esisezantsi (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Esc;</keycombo>) esikunika ukhakhayi/amathambo "
"anqamlezayo esalathisi. Nqakraza eso salathisi kwi window ukuyibulala. "
"Izibophelelo ezingundoqo ziyaboniselwa/ziyatshintsheka kwi "
"<application>&kde; Umbindi Wolawulo</application>."
